EXECUTE EVERYTHING FROM
/project
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

ACTIVATE VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT
. .venv/bin/activate
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

TEST
- ALL MODULES
python -m unittest
- SINGLE MODULE
python -m unittest test.<module-name>
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

TEST WITH COVERAGE
coverage run -m unittest
coverage html
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

LYNTING
- ALL MODULES
		pylint ./src
- SINGLE MODULE
		pylint <module-name>.py
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
RUN WSGI SERVER
gunicorn -w 4 -b 0.0.0.0 'app:create_app("<your-file>.config")'